      <title>4 decisions that turned SNL into a cultural juggernaut — and 3 mistakes</title>
      <author>Eric Deggans</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/02/13/nx-s1-5262898/saturday-night-live-50th-anniversary</link>
