      <title>Dear Life Kit: My friend kissed me and I liked it. Now he wants to take it back!</title>
      <author>Andee Tagle</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/02/13/nx-s1-5289038/dear-life-kit-friend-kissed-me-i-liked-it-he-took-back</link>
